#: document/templates/admin/document/maintenance.html:19
msgid ""
"\n"
"            Before and after upgrading Fidus Writer, you should update all "
"the documents\n"
"            of all users to the newest document version. Only do this if you "
"know that\n"
"            no user is currently editing any document!\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            Avant et après la mise à niveau de Fidus Writer, vous devez "
"mettre à jour tous les documents\n"
"            de tous les utilisateurs à la dernière version du document. Ne "
"faites cela que si vous savez que\n"
"            aucun utilisateur ne modifie actuellement aucun document!\n"
"                        "

#: document/templates/admin/document/maintenance.html:27
